<br>
For instance, we had all three Teenage Mutant Ninja turtles here on FV for a while.  While hardly original, it was obviously very fun for them and for everyone around them.  Uh, learn from what happened to them, too.  The TMNTs got nuked by a GM for using trademarked characters (ie. copying known literature).  Make up you're own and you're home free. <p>Mosushi, Lizard Master of the Fish<br>
